data.description: Come experience Florida life in this charming coastal cottage style home with a POOL! Park your boat, RV or jet skis on the OVERSIZED DRIVEWAY and your vehicle in the one-car garage. Just a short drive to Charlotte Park to access boat ramps, kayaking, bike riding, tennis, and more... This home has been tastefully updated and recently painted inside and out. Perfect for entertainment with a private pool and large screened-in lanai. Sit back relax and enjoy your backyard visitors which include beautiful birds and turtles. The kitchen has been updated with GRANITE countertops, white cabinets and newer appliances. Large dinning room of the kitchen with sliding glass doors leading to the lanai. The entire home has PORCELAIN TILES FLOORS. Both of the bathrooms have also been updated to be more functional and water efficient. This property gets plenty of natural light with its large windows, but also so private with its privacy shades installed in the living room, kitchen and bedrooms. There is plenty of storage room through the house, the kitchen has 2 pantries, plus a Ted Shed on the back of the house. AC was replaced in 2017, water heater on 2020 and roof in 2014. This community is known as laid back with easy access to canals, short drive to the beach or Fishermans Village to experience the island live with shopping, music, dinning, etc... Conveniently located near the Punta Gorda Airport making it a perfect vacation home or all year round vacation life!
